    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual, futuristic visual. On the left, a translucent human head silhouette with subtle glowing neural pathways, representing invasive BCI, with a small, sleek, futuristic microchip subtly integrated. On the right, a stylized, ergonomic wearable headband, glowing softly, representing non-invasive BCI, connected to a person's temple. In the background, a subtle, abstract representation of data flowing and converging. The overall color scheme should be sophisticated blues, purples, and greens, suggesting innovation and health, with a dynamic, forward-looking composition. The image should convey the contrast and convergence of invasive and wearable human-tech interaction, globally relevant, with subtle nods to India, US, UK, Canada, Australia via abstract, interconnected light trails.",
