    featuredImagePrompt: "A futuristic and dynamic industry-specific visual depicting the intersection of artificial intelligence and cryptocurrency. The image should feature a digital interface displaying a stylized candlestick chart for Bitcoin and Ethereum, with abstract AI elements like neural network nodes or glowing data streams overlayed. A subtle, human hand could be interacting with a holographic representation of this data, conveying assistance and control. The background should suggest a global financial landscape, perhaps with faint outlines of city skylines from New York, London, Mumbai, and Sydney. Emphasize both innovation and the volatile nature of the market with a mix of vibrant greens and reds within the data streams.",
