    featuredImagePrompt: "A conceptual visual representing global IPO market turmoil. Shattered glass fragments form a crude, abstract map of the world, with distressed stock market charts and downward trending arrows embedded within. Cracks radiate outwards from a central, subtly glowing point, symbolizing the origin of geopolitical conflict (e.g., abstract red lines or faint, blurred military-like symbols). In the background, faint, blurred outlines of iconic financial district skylines (New York, London, Mumbai) are visible. The overall mood is tense, fragile, and uncertain, using a palette of muted blues, grays, and a touch of urgent, symbolic red. The composition should be dynamic, with elements appearing to break apart, emphasizing the 'shockwaves' concept, yet remaining artistic and thought-provoking. Avoid literal war imagery or identifiable faces.",
