      probabilityWeightedOutlook: "There is a high probability that Taiwan\'s new crypto law will lead to increased market maturity and investor confidence. While short-term challenges for some VASPs are expected (medium probability), the long-term benefits of a regulated environment, including greater institutional adoption and reduced systemic risks, are likely to prevail (high probability). The overall impact is cautiously positive for the industry\'s sustainable growth.",
