      vestingAnalysis: "The Ethereum Foundation primarily holds ETH from its initial ICO, much of which is used to fund operations and grants. While there isn\'t a traditional \'vesting schedule\' like a startup, the EF\'s recent budget cuts imply a more cautious approach to spending its reserves, which could reduce selling pressure from operational needs.",
